The '''quetch pétanque player''' is an old [[Quetch]] plays pétanque together with his friend, [[Anatole]], on the pétanque field in [[Port-Ludo]].

This quetch does not help [[Twinsen]] with anything. If Twinsen walks in the middle of the field, the player continuously shouts "cheater!".

